summary: These are some cute character presets that I made out of boredom lol
descriptionHtml:
Here's a few cute character presets I made out of boredom. Hope you like them. Anyways this mod adds two presets (Ariana 1 and 2),Ariana 1 is a freckled long haired version of Ariana,Ariana 2 is a warrior version of Ariana.

To make the character look like the one i have in the shots or close to in the shots (I don't use an ENB but ENBs seem to change the look of the character a bit) Use:

Pride Of Valhalla(only .dds files):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/72586/?

Fair Skin Complexion(Only s.dds and Msn.dds,keep Pride's .dds):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?

SG Female Textures Renewal(only use Tintmask files for the makeup):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?

Nise's head mesh files for Racemenu/ECE(NiseHead17):http://www.loverslab.com/topic/77092-the-amazing-world-of-bikini-armour/

Freckle Mania 2 The Refreckeling(for dirt and freckles):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86208/?

SKSE ini pre-download(for 2048 resolution tintmasks aka higher quality overlay resolutions):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51038/?

The Coenaculi:https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35677/?

KS hairdos - Renewal(for the hairstyles that these presets use):https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?
author: BR1
